Re: 間違い探し: Can you find the mistake?
by phreadom » Thu 09.09.2010 1:31 am Well, I enjoyed trying to figure out what the sign was trying to say... but I just don't know enough yet to point out the error. I had fun trying to figure out the kanji though... I ended up using IME Pad for 2 of them. I feel silly for not knowing 自転車 and 乗る though, as I know both the vocabulary, but just hadn't learned the kanji yet (aside from 車).Thanks for the puzzle though Becki! I look forward to the explanation of the error.
