Re: 間違い探し: Can you find the mistake?
by ss » Thu 09.09.2010 3:34 am Thank you Becki. I would like to try .... ジョギングコースでの自転車に乗るのはやめましょう。Spoiler: I don't think the "の" is necessary there.ジョギングコースで自転車に乗るのはやめましょうLet's stop cycling on the jogging course
